{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775860108870,"sessionID":"ses_2867e396cffeXyILg3kxWXjsTN","part":{"id":"prt_d7982ca84001C0LOby1XyV4QsR","messageID":"msg_d7982bbfa001BFFSOxIUqTScO2","sessionID":"ses_2867e396cffeXyILg3kxWXjsTN","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_08d4aaf96cfe458cb5fbf12b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-020/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-020/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Delta Spec: AR-020 — CLI pack 命令\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: This delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the CLI pack command in `cmd/cli`.\n6: \n7: ## Base Specifications\n8: \n9: - **AR**: AR-020\n10: - **Module**: `cmd/cli`\n11: - **Language**: Python\n12: - **Size**: M\n13: \n14: ---\n15: \n16: ## Background\n17: \n18: ...\n19: \n20: ---\n21: \n22: ## Requirements\n23: \n24: ### AR-020-001: ...\n25: \n26: #### Scenario: AR-020-001-A — ...\n27: \n28: ...\n29: \n30: ---\n31: \n32: ## Acceptance Criteria\n33: \n34: - [ ] AC001: ...\n\n(End of file - total 34 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Delta Spec: AR-020 — CLI pack 命令\n\n## Overview\n\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the CLI pack command in `cmd/cli`.\n\n## Base Specifications\n\n- **AR**: AR-020\n- **Module**: `cmd/cli`\n- **Language**: Python\n- **Size**: M\n\n---\n\n## Background\n\n...\n\n---","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-020/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775860108860,"end":1775860108868}}}}
